0c2798c20d96b91648e3101282d8e","tid":777813,"uid":200505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:24:07.000Z","msg":"其實成個香港社都好有病，大家有得走好快d走。<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">來生不做香港人</span></span>"},{"pid":"c057f6e1b071fbc91db35be824ed43169b654b32","tid":777813,"uid":11973,"like":2,"dislike":31,"score":-29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:24:40.000Z","msg":"好心啲傳媒唔好成日報呢啲令人心噏嘅新聞啦<br />\n咁同渲染自殺有乜分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人生在世<br />\n辦法總比困難多<br />\n點解唔可以好好珍惜生命<br />\n有勇氣去死竟然冇勇氣去面對?<br />\n一時睇唔開鑽牛角尖就白白犧牲咗寶貴嘅生命真係好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實可以活喺香港已經係好大嘅福氣<br />\n試諗吓地球上有幾多人生活喺戰亂飢荒國家每日同死神搏鬥食都冇啖好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d86b4e97f4c46b4dfa7aa45472c6a34e4b4b3a","tid":777813,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:25:26.000Z","msg":"福氣到極"},{"pid":"a4c624c97759f7900c58b0ec13bfb0168d6cc033","tid":777813,"uid":106211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:34:19.000Z","msg":"香港超越左東京同韓國未"},{"pid":"6ba2304a9ca00179cebd7cabf4968bcc54809126","tid":777813,"uid":199211,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:35:06.000Z","msg":"港大私樓都自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實啲廢中可能無屌錯 以前環境差佢都無自殺 有層私樓走去自殺"},{"pid":"182abf22531f24dfa9acefedbc630f367afcca26","tid":777813,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:41:01.000Z","msg":"6單...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee365446aab04b7605143529f27171ecd8966d3","tid":777813,"uid":29230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:45:03.000Z","msg":"7月了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2ec71c1aec7f4dbcf844a16903c10f08ffce9f","tid":777813,"uid":42767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:47:08.000Z","msg":"邊止咁少, 無報出黎"},{"pid":"5371436b9d3a4c9368687286b52fb7c2dc7ced9d","tid":777813,"uid":192263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:49:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52be75410b4c2b95e3f1c124a9d20e30be87189c","tid":777813,"uid":143454,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:50:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb9a9f2a4f4abe3d4fe6a9f54585271554a18198","tid":777813,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:52:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48f964127b9a08a0a609e1d92cd1cb88b180b70d","tid":777813,"uid":143454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:52:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9ae9a8e100be9096d6767df158ba7cc3a511da7","tid":777813,"uid":117200,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"呢個城市太痴線<br />\n每日150分薄資源<br />\n政府著重錢唔重心身生活健康<br />\nM型社會<br />\n人工十年不變<br />\n暴發戶/黑錢黨掃晒d樓搶日用品黎炒<br />\n無自由權言論權<br />\n人與人之間監控<br />\n生活質素20年越黎越差<br />\n<br />\nchild登仔成日笑台灣日本,但係連泰國都就黎好過你<br />\n講緊唔係賺錢呢d數字遊戲,係人與生俱來嘅生命享受權"},{"pid":"083c3c212da48111b3565fec40ffee4b825aa2f6","tid":777813,"uid":114275,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"52be75410b4c2b95e3f1c124a9d20e30be87189c","tid":777813,"uid":143454,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ed9024f87ea3985882969bfb6a9253f19a8ac430","tid":777813,"uid":114275,"like":7,"dislike":33,"score":-26,"quote":{"pid":"19d2b92c736555f9d0891d965e47f9bc524777d2","tid":777813,"uid":143621,"like":75,"dislike":4,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T10:25:50.000Z","msg":"咁點解你唔做啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解人地無曬希望要自殺死都仲要比你地消費啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n既然係善事點解你又唔帶頭日行一善啊請問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不如你去做啦 我係呢到拉隊幫你爭取紀念日 你又點睇啊？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T10:32:17.000Z","msg":"因為我未想死囉咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n乜撚樣消費姐 人都死啦 介意乜野姐<br />\n<br />\n都係當幫自己積福或者出啖氣姐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己就唔想死住亦無勇氣去做偉人<br />\n<br />\n所以先拜託 d 有勇氣嘅人<br />\n<br />\n死有輕於鴻毛重於泰山<br />\n<br />\n自己決定架姐"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:50:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"因為人地無做過 d 對你有利嘅事<br />\n<br />\n所以你就要避免做 d 對人有利嘅事？<br />\n<br />\n咁樣就 fair ?  <br />\n<br />\n生死都要貫徹香港人魚蛋精神？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我講咗 死你可以選擇寂靜無聲咁死<br />\n<br />\n就正如你在生嘅時候寂靜無聲咁存在<br />\n<br />\n或者你可以選擇另一種死法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔想死嘅就努力生存<br />\n<br />\n想死嘅就自己諗下點揀"},{"pid":"4f5fc4cb9e7de5cfab8522dd057b5f8b9451329b","tid":777813,"uid":143454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:07:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad077812df75fb53eb8cf9ffcd9967ce2651bdcc","tid":777813,"uid":18894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:09:24.000Z","msg":"其實唔止咁少<br />\n我果幢今日都有人跳"},{"pid":"81d44bbc9c56896344195e67bcb0a5c4d3130541","tid":777813,"uid":180632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:09:36.000Z","msg":"好想喊"},{"pid":"6697bdf54a4fbaae5ac1ae5cb887647793f8c2fd","tid":777813,"uid":26106,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:11:37.000Z","msg":"睇到d留言真係笑左<br />\n人地要自殺已經絕望到仆街<br />\n仲想自殺既人都要拎著數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db3e2ada5e2569028f89a45dd53201a097da8f4","tid":777813,"uid":121454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:12:04.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"1faf55c4a4223a4e9743d16273f8b81527215e38","tid":777813,"uid":143454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score